g2:c.METHOD.g2:a.TEXT: invalidate-item-cache (Self: class class-instance-event-listener {The listener to be notified of an event}, Event: class class-instance-event {The event}) {This method will notify all listeners of changes made by any one view.} begin end

items-deleted (Self: class class-instance-event-listener {The listener to be notified of an event}, Event: class class-instance-event {The event}) {This method will notify all listeners of changes made by any one view.} begin end

items-added (Self: class class-instance-event-listener {The listener to be notified of an event}, Event: class class-instance-event {The event}) {This method will notify all listeners of changes made by any one view.} begin end
invalidate-item-cache (CacheListener: class _ievlnr-internal-state-monitor, Event: class class-instance-event) begin delete CacheListener; end
items-deleted (CacheListener: class _ievlnr-internal-state-monitor, Event: class class-instance-event) begin call invalidate-item-cache (CacheListener, Event); end
delete-event (Event: class class-instance-event) begin delete Event; end

items-added (CacheListener: class _ievlnr-internal-state-monitor, Event: class class-instance-event) begin conclude that the _ievlnr-state-data of CacheListener = concatenate (the _ievlnr-state-data of CacheListener, the event-list of the event-data of Event); end
